JDP 1. Bitmap Frenzy

Purpose
-	Improve skills of working with specification
-	Improve TDD skills
Description
Given 2 command line parameters (input_file_path , output_file_path), program should read the BMP file from input_file_path , reverse the image by 180 degrees and save the result  to output_file_path. The code should be written using TDD approach.
Restrictions
No image processing libraries should be used.
Resources
BMP Bitmap file format specification http://www.dragonwins.com/domains/getteched/bmp/bmpfileformat.htm
References
Steve Freeman: "Growing Object-Oriented Software, Guided by Tests"
